    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-12-08T11:35:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-12-08T11:35:00-05:00" n="223"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d223">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">891.00/1959: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Iran</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tehran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-12-08T20:00:00+03:25"
                            >December 8, 1942—8 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received December 9—9:16 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>425. My 424. Crowd is now out of hand and rioting has developed on widespread and
                    severe scale. Shopping area is being looted by uncontrolled mobs. Police and
                    army are coming belatedly into action. Damage is heavy and there have been
                    casualties.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
